{"address1": "Tower-B", "address2": "9th Floor Prima Bay, Gate No.5 Saki Vihar Road, Powai", "city": "Mumbai", "zip": "400072", "country": "India", "phone": "91 22 6693 1600", "fax": "91 22 6693 1627", "website": "https://www.cemindia.co.in", "industry": "Engineering & Construction", "industryKey": "engineering-construction", "industryDisp": "Engineering & Construction", "sector": "Industrials", "sectorKey": "industrials", "sectorDisp": "Industrials", "longBusinessSummary": "Cemindia Projects Limited provides construction and civil engineering contracting services in India. The company constructs maritime structures, including jetties, dolphins, service platforms, quay, berths on concrete and steel piles, solid gravity type wharf structures, ship lifts, dry docks, wet basins, and inclined berths; mass rapid transport systems (MRTs); airports; highways, bridges, and flyovers; foundations and specialized engineering works comprising geotechnical investigations, piling, diaphragm walling, slope stabilization, sandwicks/band drains, vibrofloatation stone columns, drilling and grouting, rock/soil anchors repairs, colcrete, gunite/shotcrete, grouted mattress, box pushing, tube heading, microtunneling, and rehabilitation and underpinning services; and dams and tunnels, TBM, M-TBM, NATM Tunnels, Box Pushing Tunnels. It also offers breakwater and piled approach trestles, steel piles and bored casts, undersea ground improvement, dredging and land reclamation, and coastal erosion protection and rock bund services, as well as foundation and specialist engineering services. In addition, the company engages in the civil works for refinery, petrochemical, power, steel, and fertilizer plants; design, construction, supply, installation, and commissioning of pipelines; operation of water and wastewater treatment plants, and pumping stations; and develops data center to cater to deliver cutting-edge, integrated solutions tailored to critical sectors. It serves the state and central government departments, ministries, local municipal bodies, and private clients. The company was formerly known as ITD Cementation India Limited and changed its name to Cemindia Projects Limited in August 2025. Cemindia Projects Limited was founded in 1931 and is based in Mumbai, India. As of August 8, 2025, Cemindia Projects Limited operates as a subsidiary of Renew Exim DMCC.", "fullTimeEmployees": 2769, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Jayanta  Basu", "age": 61, "title": "MD & Executive Director", "yearBorn": 1964, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 53430175, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Rahul  Neogi", "title": "Senior VP, Compliance Officer & Company Secretary", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Nitesh  Sharma", "title": "Joint Executive VP & CFO", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Rupak  Sarkar", "title": "Executive VP & COO", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Manish  Kumar", "title": "Executive VP & CTO", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. KR  Senthilnathan", "title": "VP and Head of Business Development & Marketing", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. V. R. Gopakumar", "title": "Joint Executive VP & Head Human Resources", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Sunder L. Chanchlani", "title": "Executive VP & Chief Commercial Officer", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Shivanagouda N. Patil", "title": "Executive Vice President", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Schon  Sarkar", "title": "Joint Executive Vice President", "fiscalYear": 2025, "exercisedValue": 0, "